ated to maintaining a rigorous credit analysis process that drives its disciplined approach to investing and asset growth over the course of its over twenty year history black diamond has developed a consistent philosophy of investing in debt securities that offer both structural protection and substantial underlying assets this philosophy enables the company to protect against downside risk while capitalizing on both broad market and individual company volatility   black diamond capital management llc all rights reserved black diamond capital management  contact us black diamond capital management about us  values  investment philosophy  contact us contact us one sound shore drivesuite greenwich ct phone  email infobdcmcom   black diamond capital management llc all rights reserved ﻿ black diamond capital management  our investment philosophy black diamond capital management about us  values  investment philosophy  contact us investmentphilosophy black diamond was founded in  with a bedrock investment philosophy that has remained consistent over the past  years and continues to guide the firm today the philosophy encompasses the following key principles focus on areas of expertise – black diamond’s management team and investment professionals have decades of experience in the credit distressed debt and private equity markets and have particular expertise in underwriting trading restructuring and managing controlled distressed investments the company applies its superior intellectual capital investment experience and restructuring knowhow to inform its focused approach to carefully selected debt securities that offer both structural protection and substantial underlying assets this focused approach to investing emphasizes black diamond’s competitive advantages and enables it to provide superior returns to its investors which at the end of the day is the firm’s primary focus managing risk – black diamond maintains a rigorously disciplined credit analysis process which is designed to protect its investments from excessive downside risk the company reinforces this process by informing its bottoms up credit analysis approach to investing with extensive macro credit market analysis ensuring that it can navigate the risks associated not only with its individual investments but also the broader market seizing opportunity – black diamond believes that many of the best investment opportunities arise from volatility in the market and in individual companies stressed and distressed situations with this in mind black diamond maintains a discipline when it comes to the deployment of capital but it is tenacious when an appealing investment has been identified alignment of interests – black diamond is dedicated to providing superior returns and a client experience that treats its investors as true partners in doing so black diamond believes that it is only successful if its interests are fully aligned with the interests of its various investors as such a singleminded focus on the investor underpins every investment decision the company makes   black diamond capital management llc all rights reserved ﻿ black diamond capital management  our values black diamond capital management about us  values  investment philosophy  contact us values black diamond is guided by five core values that shape the company’s culture and guide the way the business operates intelligence we offer superior intellectual capital investment experience and restructuring knowhow experience we have an extensive track record that shows consistent success in underwriting trading restructuring and managing performing stressed and control distressed investments through multiple market cycles focus we maintain a focus on disciplined investing in our areas of expertise and successfully combine bottoms up credit analysis with an indepth knowledge of the credit system passion we are passionate about our investors and our investments and remain at all times focused on delivering superior returns patience we have the patience and strategic fortitude to maintain a consistent focus on longterm investment returns and the sustainable growth of our company   black diamond capital management llc all rights reserved black diamond capital management llc  lake forest  il  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory il lake forest management consulting services management consulting services black diamond capital management llc b black diamond capital management llc claim this business  n field dr ste  lake forest il  get directions   wwwbdcmcom business info founded  incorporated annual revenue  employee count  industries management consulting services contacts steven deckoff contact business your email address subject message send message company summary black diamond capital management llc was founded in  black diamond capital management llc specializes in management consulting services verified status unverified address unverified last verified  phone unverified payment method unverified view full report similar businesses nearby our similar businesses nearby shows similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review profile competitive landscape our competitive landscape shows how this business compares to similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review profile payments accepted no data hours sunday   monday   tuesday   wednesday   thursday   friday   saturday   b view additional data select from over  networks below to view available data about this business if this data is unavailable or inaccurate and you own or represent this business click here for more information on how you may be able to correct it credibility review google facebookcom yellowbookcom bingcom yellowpagescom merchantcircle tele atlas tomtom twittercom aol mapquest yahoo local applesiri groupon hot